    Example: layerDefinitions.setLayerDefinition(0, "POPULATION > 5000000"); layerDefinitions.setLayerDefinition(0, "AREA > 100000"); dynamicMapServiceLayer.setLayerDefinitions(layerDefinitions); Note that the array indices 0 and 5 are valid layer IDs, and POPULATION and AREA are valid attribute fields associated with the respective layers.
